  "title": "P8_为什么微信运动不会计步，或者计步数一直不增长？",
  "answer": " <p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:15.75pt\">有两个问题会导致该问题</p> <p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:15.75pt;orphans: auto; text-align:start;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\">微信配置白名单延迟，导致手机型号未进入微信运动的白名单，此时需要重新退出微信然后登陆.</p> <p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:15.75pt;orphans: auto; text-align:start;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\">微信应用存在读取计步数有问题，导致计步数一直为0或者计步到某个数值以后一直不增长。此时有如下两种处理办法：</p> <p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:15.75pt;orphans: auto; text-align:start;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\">(1).查看微信是否有新版本，更新到新版本解决该问题,然后退出微信重新登录。</p> <p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:15.75pt;orphans: auto; text-align:start;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\">(2).先取消关注微信运动公众号，然后重新关注微信运动公众号即可。取消关注微信运动公号方法如下：</p> <p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:15.75pt;orphans: auto; text-align:start;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\">![http://w3.huawei.com/tkbmng/ha-i/6cbe4_d6xlc.png](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150914092307611001.gif)  ![http://w3.huawei.com/tkbmng/ha-i/6cbe5_jgoo9.png](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150914092308292002.gif)     ![http://w3.huawei.com/tkbmng/ha-i/6cbe6_aixeg.png](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150914092308294003.jpg)</p> <p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:15.75pt;orphans: auto; text-align:start;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\">如果用户还需要了解微信运动的其他FAQ，建议用户在微信运动公众号中输入帮助，然后发送，微信运动会有FAQ推送：</p> <p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:15.75pt;orphans: auto; text-align:start;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\">![http://w3.huawei.com/tkbmng/ha-i/6cbe7_yj8ya.png](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150914092308283004.gif)</p>",
